# N=2: a win completed by the OTHER player's move.
# A stacks disk 3 on pole 3 but leaves disk 1 on the shared pole, so A is not
# yet winning. When B lifts that disk off the shared pole it clears the shared
# pole and completes A's win on B's turn -- which is why the engine checks both
# players after every move.
n 2
A lift 1
A place 2
A lift 1
A place 3
B lift 2
